        <Parent_String>commode steps (steps) [300003315], steps (staircase units) [300003312], steps and step components [300052381], stair components [300003284], stairs and stair components [300073803], circulation elements [300003217], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
